The poor rains have also adversely affected other crops, such as sorghum, soybeans, groundnuts, tobacco and cotton, the Agriculture Ministry reported at the end of February
The problem with memory chips is that they are all based on the same, well known design standards, so they are easy to copy and inexpensive to manufacture
Customized chips, however, are designed for a specific customer, manufactured in small quantities and expensive relative to standard chips
Computer markets are increasingly looking to customized chips because they are difficult to copy, thus making the final product harder to clone as well
Intel will customize those designs and sell them to others
Industry analysts noted that it is far different to design a mass market item than a customized chip that requires a close working relationship with the customer
A much faster turnarouond time, and much lower development costs, will be required for customized chips if the firm is to succeed
